        "content": "<p>The issue is that when you write <code>contradiction : 1 &lt; 1</code>, Lean interprets <code>1</code> as a natural integer because it has no way to know you use it as a real number, but then you compare it to real numbers, that's why there's a problem. If you write instead <code>contradiction : (1 : ℝ) &lt; 1</code> it should work fine.</p>",
